    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想了解《恶霸反抗军》以及更多 Hooded Horse 策略类游戏信息与福利，QQ频道搜索:Hooded Horse 加入我们 或关注 bilibili 官方账号 @HoodedHorse。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/abcafd46aed9d5fc2daae017be8558a4.poster.avif?t=1771525034\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/abcafd46aed9d5fc2daae017be8558a4.webm?t=1771525034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/abcafd46aed9d5fc2daae017be8558a4.mp4?t=1771525034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帝国已经统治太久，在它的治下整个世界满目疮痍！宁静的林地何在？潺潺的溪流何在？不绝于耳的婴儿欢笑和家庭的温馨何在？这个世界完全陷入了前所未有的恶劣境地！霸主啊，如此暴政必须终结，而您麾下这群怪物般的恶棍正是实现此目标的最佳团队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Bosslords》是一款roguelite自动战斗游戏，您将率领世间勤勉的底层人物和恶棍——指挥哥布林和食尸鬼，唤起亡者，跨越海陆空展开征途，直面帝国派来追剿您的千军万马。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/83838c1dda70537c9ac9d42f7fcf94ff.avif?t=1771525034\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/f6b19d2f8cce9c360295ac94ff8558da.poster.avif?t=1771525034\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/f6b19d2f8cce9c360295ac94ff8558da.webm?t=1771525034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/f6b19d2f8cce9c360295ac94ff8558da.mp4?t=1771525034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择一位霸主执掌大权，每位霸主都拥有各自的故事线、技能和升级树，率领独特的初始军队、运用奇门法术，踏上你的征战之旅。虽然每位霸主都能招募多种单位并运用不同策略，但他们各自拥有独特的优势、偏好和专属机制：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>哥布林将军</strong>依靠训练有素的大批哥布林军队，能将弱小的喽啰转变为纪律严明的强悍部队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死灵法师</strong>可带领精英卫队，即使战死亦能在每场战斗后复苏，并运用强化的死灵法术召唤和强化更多战士</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>军阀</strong>率领一支规模虽小却精锐的老兵部队，以提升的属性弥补数量上的不足</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>法师</strong>擅长召唤生物参战，凭借更强大的法术和元素生物来支援作战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>驯龙师</strong>统率一支蜥蜴人军队，可将其训练为强悍战士——或喂食给他的龙宠以增强其力量，因为这条龙可以通过吞噬一切来变得更强</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/8b7deebf5c155ab4edf47759720beafc.avif?t=1771525034\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/a672e66d4586e9096479e630d4a84075.poster.avif?t=1771525034\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/a672e66d4586e9096479e630d4a84075.webm?t=1771525034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/a672e66d4586e9096479e630d4a84075.mp4?t=1771525034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纵使您目标崇高、热血澎湃，若无军队相伴，亦将一事无成。王国各地的酒馆和商铺中挤满了待时而动的潜在革命者——只等遇见明主（加上足够的报酬），您甚至能在荒野中寻得徘徊求索荣耀的迷途之魂。队伍中的兽人鼓手能加速我方单位的攻击，女妖可令敌人麻痹，而僵尸旗手则能提升队友的生命力。您会依赖后排列阵射击的骷髅卫队，同时让蜘蛛以蛛网延缓敌军推进吗？抑或您的军队以匕首刺客和魁梧牛头怪为中坚，辅以哥布林军士来提升战力？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/35c79ae407432ca097efd05b8d2ae1e6.avif?t=1771525034\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/a0cfbbd599016ccf17e34a0df948a545.poster.avif?t=1771525034\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/a0cfbbd599016ccf17e34a0df948a545.webm?t=1771525034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537440/extras/a0cfbbd599016ccf17e34a0df948a545.mp4?t=1771525034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若没有几招压箱底的绝技，还算什么霸主？从哥布林将军的火铳手枪，到死灵法师将敌人转化为己方骷髅战士的诅咒，独特能力让每位霸主脱颖而出！旅途中收集卷轴，解锁强大法术以助力仆从战斗——升起火焰之墙，驾驭雷霆之力，召唤天降陨石，或令大地震裂！用特殊物品进一步强化部队——再生药水能使阵线在危急关头存续，而一份足量的粘液果酱可将倒下的盟友转化为粘液怪物！无论是为武器淬毒，还是诅咒敌人的灵魂，当个反派的感觉可真不错。</p>",
